	end

function Start(idActorPlayer, snoglyph)

	ID_GROUNDEFFECT = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, FX_GROUND_EFFECT, true)
		
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

		DropEssance(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	end	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, snoglyph)

		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idActorPlayer, ID_PROXY, EG_ATTRACTOR)
	end
end

unk_c47e01a:
local function ResetGroundEffectSizeAndPlay(idActor, flSize)

	
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idActor, ID_GROUNDEFFECT)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idActor, flSize)
	ID_GROUNDEFFECT = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActor, FX_GROUND_EFFECT, true)

end

local function DropEssance(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
			-- Spawn item from killer to killed (extend the line)
			--Check if killer and killed are valid in case of things like wall affix.
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorKiller) then
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorKilled) then
			local ptItemPos = Hydra.PositionOffsetFromPosition(
				Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idActorKilled), 
				Hydra.ActorGetPosition(idActorKiller),
				Hydra.GetRandomFloat(2.5, 3), true)
				
			-- Extra Random
			ptItemPos = Hydra.PositionOffsetRandomly(ptItemPos, 0.5, 1)
			
			-- Spawn the item at desinated position
			local ptItemFacing = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(idActorKiller)
			local idItemProxy = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_GENERIC_PROXY, ptItemPos, ptItemFacing, false, 0, 0)
	
			local tItems = Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idItemProxy, TREASURECLASS_SOUL, idActorKiller)
	
			-- Spawn an instantly attractar
			Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idItemProxy, 3)
			Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(idActorKilled, 0.8)
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idActorKilled, idItemProxy, EG_ATTRACTOR)
			
			-- Clear the proxy
			Hydra.Wait(3)
			Hydra.ActorDelete(idItemProxy)
		end
	end
end
